title: Overlord of Insects
description: Overlord of Insects Manhua Having been transported into a world where everyone is a Job-Changer, Jiang Chen awakened the Insect Domination System! The little insects can evolve, attack, and extract talents! Most importantly, they can breed invincible natural disasters! 我，虫族主宰 , Overlord of Insects, The Zerg Overlord, The King of the Insects, The Zerg Dominator, Supreme Zerg Lord
